snippet.title: Gene Machine
snippet.description:
Howdy.

Gene Machine is a series that takes a look at misleading, fake, and downright terrible mobile game ads, and analyzes exactly what in the ad makes it one of the mentioned descriptions. 

The ultimate goal of this channel is to help shed some light on the ongoing problem that is fake mobile game ads, and as a result, help take part in the eventual crackdown on them. 

🔴Please check the links below for my twitter, discord, and twitch!🔴

For business inquires, please use the email down below.
